&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( hindi : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ; school ) is a 2010 indian drama film that stars shahid kapoor , ayesha takia , shraddha arya , ali haji , sushant singh and nana patekar and is directed by milind ukey . the story revolves around children on a school campus . it comments on the indian education system and its shortcomings . kapoor plays an english and music teacher . it is inspired by the marathi film &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , also directed by milind ukey . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; opened on 16 april 2010 to mixed reviews .